    "As shown in Tab.",
    "3, SSH consistently delivers superior or comparable performance across all evaluation metrics, while requiring significantly fewer trainable parameters.",
    "For GPT-2 Medium, SSH matches the highest BLEU score (70.1) and outperforms other methods in NIST (8.82), METEOR (47.2), ROUGE-L (71.9), and CIDEr (2.54), all with 10.3% fewer parameters than LoRA and 25% fewer than FourierFT.",
